{"tid":1888814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日香港醫學會前會長蔡堅屌港共屌到啪啪聲！","createTime":"2020-02-20T12:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T15:15:25.000Z","uid":36494,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"34cee9f91858d377f410d37787a33fa6e20c8cd8","tid":1888814,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T12:03:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200220/6OUU23JIOEFLPPZ4HN4WYKN7BQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200220%2F6OUU23JIOEFLPPZ4HN4WYKN7BQ%2F&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=6f0af951\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200220%2F6OUU23JIOEFLPPZ4HN4WYKN7BQ%2F&h=9ad2d03d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200220/6OUU23JIOEFLPPZ4HN4WYKN7BQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄如下：<br />\n<br />\n香港醫學會前會長蔡堅指，社區已有隱形帶菌者出現，市民應戴口罩，又說認同以喜靈洲等離島作為隔離營，但政府拒封關，「幾多個喜靈洲都唔夠」。<br />\n<br />\n認為政府應把新型肺炎納入勞保保障醫護，並為使用大量裝備的私家診所提供支援，「不過『現兜兜』向市民派10,000蚊仲好」。<br />\n<br />\n他提醒市民不要盡信數字，「將中國啲數字乘10倍我就信」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蔡對於有聲音着公立醫院醫護要把裝備「慳啲用」，「聽到係好反感，何來有證據證明佢哋唔係慳啲用？講呢啲嘢時有無用腦，我唔知道」。<br />\n<br />\n「尤其係當我哋（政府）唔封關，幾多喜靈洲（做隔離營）都無用，可能開放軍營仲實際」"},{"pid":"d1c8a8241bf4191bbfad228e169e41fa37071454","tid":1888814,"uid":188685,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T12:05:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>每日to-DO List</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. Twitter 戰線<br />\n2. 去tvb廣告商fb洗版<br />\n3.幫襯黃色經濟圈</span><br />\n4.壯大黃圈youtuber, Dislike 藍絲Youtuber<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hRqjURW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhRqjURW.jpg&h=d2027af9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VVLv1wX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVVLv1wX.jpg&h=95d611f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=